title: ADVICE: texting your ex, adulting + moving on

description:
Brooke and Danielle are solo this week and catching up!  The gals also dive into some advice topics and tackle questions like dealing with post grad life, how to get over someone you never *really* dated, should you text your ex, staying fit in college/post grad and more!
